This project is an AI-powered code translator that converts code between Python and JavaScript using a lightweight HuggingFace model.
It features a clean Streamlit interface and runs efficiently on CPU without needing external APIs.
Designed for learners and developers, the tool supports core code constructs like functions, loops, and conditionals, making it ideal for education, syntax comparison, and cross-language development. 
Whether you're a student, teacher, or full-stack coder, this app offers a fast, simple way to understand and translate code using open-source AI.
